            whileInView={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
            transition={{ duration: 0.8 }}
            className="text-center mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
          >
            {/* SEO: H2 tag - Descriptive heading with keywords */}
            <h2 className="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-[#355E3B] mb-6">
              Why Choose Organic Products Pakistan from Origiganics by Wallian
            </h2>
            <div className="text-lg text-[#6F4E37] text-left space-y-4">
              <p>
                At <strong>Origiganics by Wallian</strong>, we believe that what you consume should be as pure as nature intended. 
                Our commitment to providing <strong>100% organic products Pakistan</strong> stems from a deep understanding that 
                chemical-free, natural products are essential for your health and well-being.
              </p>
              <p>
                Every product in our collection—from our premium <strong>organic food</strong> and nutrient-rich dry fruits to our 
                cold-pressed <strong>organic oils</strong>—is carefully sourced from certified organic farms across Pakistan. We work 
                directly with local farmers who share our vision of sustainable agriculture and chemical-free farming practices.
              </p>
              <p>
                Our <strong>home made products</strong> are crafted with traditional methods passed down through generations, ensuring 
                authenticity and superior quality. Whether you're looking for <strong>natural products Pakistan</strong> for your 
                family's daily nutrition or seeking <strong>chemical-free organic products</strong> for a healthier lifestyle, 
                Origiganics by Wallian is your trusted partner.
              </p>
              <p>
                We understand that modern life exposes us to countless harmful chemicals. That's why we're dedicated to offering a 
                pure alternative—products that nourish your body without compromising your health. From the fertile valleys of Hunza 
                to the rich orchards of Kashmir, we bring you nature's finest bounty, delivered fresh to your doorstep anywhere in Pakistan.
              </p>
            </div>
